{"type": "article", "id": 21895, "title": "pinch的天然材料系列家具", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-04T07:30:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 32, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122258sR8MU1NT2kiruw4E.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这套家具系列来自伦敦的设计工作室 pinch，他们使用了天然的材料。咖啡桌的表面近似大理石，最下面是深灰色的，混合了蓝色和土黄色，慢慢渐变到了白色，很有雕塑感。这种雕塑感延续到了躺椅，像是一个人侧卧着。而折叠凳 imo 则更具实用性，它可以挂在墙上，不同的木材对应了不同的颜色和质感，其中限量的绿色使用了冷衫，非常亮丽。<a href=\"http://pinchdesign.com/products/nim\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071222551ftGcAdRp5w6T27U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68215159\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071222563u8qaOght5AoMGkJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.80317848\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px; height: 245px; width: 375px; left: 589px; top: 1114px;\" class=\"dragged\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071222560pU4ltYT8rGKDdoH.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65281174\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071222572IehBTDmw3rFc9p0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.81173594\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122258BLnwYHEZlFocdya6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75550122\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}